{"tid":2460884,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"用金正恩嘅經歷嚟寫一套輕小說有冇得諗？","createTime":"2021-03-25T06:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T06:57:42.000Z","uid":305269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35ab4f0a8b7e4afb06fb1043ee71e622fa9126b9","tid":2460884,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"金正日過世後，他的三子金正恩繼位。北韓政府也開始為他建立形象，宣傳文件稱金正恩在3歲就會開槍，9歲時能射中移動的目標。此外，他3歲就懂開車，不到8歲時就能駕駛大貨車狂馳120公里，且平安的抵達目的地。還有，金正恩「沒有不會的運動，籃球勝過一般職業選手，6歲開始學會騎馬，騎術比騎手還要厲害」，同時他16歲時，便寫了一篇關於韓戰的論文，顯示出他卓越的治軍能力。金正恩為了慶祝自己1月8日的生日，向北韓全國小學學生及幼兒園和托兒所兒童送去了糖果糕點。為方便他們及時收到，金正恩下令出動飛機為全國10歲以下的兒童們分發糖果。報導指，這一傳統沿襲其祖父金日成，舉動旨在維持「慷慨、有愛心的國家領袖」形象，同時也在加強「年輕領袖的個人崇拜」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%2581%25A9&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=bf816f5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n經典龍傲天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無職轉生~到了異世界就要統治國家~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd10db83b21cd5f7f5d4643df3f69589f342fca","tid":2460884,"uid":391029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"Steam都有隻game叫Sex with Stalin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bed95cf94971ea80a1a273b210ad0c06c5ab46","tid":2460884,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd10db83b21cd5f7f5d4643df3f69589f342fca","tid":2460884,"uid":391029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re